- ðŸš€ Asynchronous event handling capabilities
- ðŸ› ï¸ Easy to use and integrate
- ðŸ“¦ Zero dependencies
- ðŸ”’ Thread-safe event distribution

## Installation

```bash
# Using pip
pip install eventspype

# Using poetry
poetry add eventspype
```

